  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Breakfast here is buffet style. In keeping with the English history of the hotel, it includes a typical English breakfast options like scrambled eggs and bacon. Have it each morning on the roof terrace, where you have the most amazing views of the coast. </p>
<p><strong>St George Restaurant by Heinz Beck</strong> is the Ashbee's one Michelin star restaurant. They serve modern Sicilian style cuisine, made using fresh seasonal produce from the island. Main courses like 'c<span>atch of the day' with lime potatoes, anchovy sauce, olive chips and rocket have us dreaming of being back there. </span>For a really special dining experience we'd recommend giving the tasting menu a try - the favours the chef creates are delicious.</p>
<p><strong>The Roof Terrace</strong> is where you'll have breakfast each morning. It's filled with light through the floor-to-ceiling windows and has stunning views of the coast. </p>
<p><strong>Pool Bar </strong>has relaxed setting beside the pool, so after a refreshing swim you can enjoy drinks or a light lunch outside while enjoying the views. </p>
<p><strong>The Ashbee Bar </strong>has a great selection of spirits, cocktails, wines, craft beers and soft drinks. Relax in the comfy chairs surrounded by interesting artworks and catch up on the days activities with a drink in hand. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
