  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Rooms</strong> are located on the first and second floor with windows overlooking the pretty courtyard. They have modern amenities including air conditioning, TV, minibar, safe and hairdryer. Rooms are individually designed and differ in style and furnishings. They sleep up to two people.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms </strong>are large and bright with lovely garden views. They sleep up to two people and are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms </strong>have a terrace with a table and chairs. They sleep up to two people and are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Suites </strong>have tailor-made furniture, are bright and airy and some have sea views. These rooms sleep up to three people and are available on request, please call to book. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
